name: 雪莉·Q
introduction: Shelley Q is an actress and singer who was born and raised on a farm in Western Australia. After gaining local fame as a singer and performer (frequently taking the stage during halftime at AFL games), Shelley broke through to an international audience landing the lead role of Karissa in the US social media thriller film 1 Million Followers, after responding to a world-wide casting call. With her film debut around the corner, she is a star on the rise as an exciting new face to the American film industry.
